376912	eng	That experience guides my conviction that partnership between America and Islam must be based on what Islam is, not what it isn't. And I consider it part of my responsibility as President of the United States to fight against negative stereotypes of Islam wherever they appear.	saeb	2010-04-08 07:48:33	2010-08-26 20:24:55
