3955438	eng	After much debate, it was decided that to be a planet in our solar system, an object must be in orbit around the Sun, have enough mass so that it has become round in shape due to its own gravity, and have cleared out its orbital path around the Sun.	Hybrid	2015-03-13 22:44:50	2015-03-13 22:44:50
