6212541	eng	The Gods assented to her prayer, and transformed her into a bird: in which shape, as in her former one, she abides in the mountains, and delights in singing. Her notes bespeak her misfortune, for she is calling her wandering cows.	Hybrid	2017-08-27 13:42:01	2017-08-27 13:42:01
6212542	eng	Such were the delights which summer brought them, but when the autumn came, and the black grapes were covered with a thick bloom, some pirates of Tyre, who had put to sea in a Carian barque, so that they might not be taken for foreigners, approached the coast, and landed, armed with swords and bucklers.	Hybrid	2017-08-27 13:42:22	2017-08-27 13:44:20
