6212588	eng	However, as soon as Daphnis and Chloe came in view of the animals and called to them in their usual manner and sounded their pipes, the sheep sprang up and began to browse, while the goats skipped about as if exulting in the return of their herdsman.	Hybrid	2017-08-27 13:56:38	2017-08-27 13:56:38
