6785667	eng	"Safe could Antenor pass th' Illyrian shore / through Danaan hosts, and realms Liburnian gain, / and climb Timavus and her springs explore, / where through nine mouths, with roaring surge, the main / bursts from the sounding rocks and deluges the plain."	carlosalberto	2018-03-20 20:45:59	2018-03-20 20:45:59
