6789616	eng	Those clothe with awe / the Senate; there they choose the judges for the law. / These delve the port; the broad foundations there / they lay for theatres of ample space, / and columns, hewn from marble rocks, prepare, / tall ornaments, the future stage to grace.	carlosalberto	2018-03-22 21:14:18	2018-03-22 21:18:42
