6804528	eng	"But Capys and the rest, of sounder mind, / urge us to tumble in the rolling tide / the doubtful gift, for treachery designed, / or burn with fire, or pierce the hollow side, / and probe the caverns where the Danaans hide."	carlosalberto	2018-03-28 15:07:46	2018-03-28 15:07:46
