7880000	eng	Joseph answered: This is the interpretation of the dream: The three branches are yet three days, after which Pharaoh will remember thy service, and will restore thee to thy former place: and thou shalt present him the cup according to thy office, as before thou was wont to do.	carlosalberto	2019-04-30 16:21:05	2019-05-14 17:28:39
